# WEB-01

## Title
Selected license is not preserved in URL

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Open capital.com
2. Select SCA license
3. Open Italy 40 page
4. Click Ferrari

## Expected
SCA URL (en-ae)

## Actual
FCA URL (en-gb)

## Severity
Major
